teo.isgci.db

Class DataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • teo.isgci.db.DataSet

  • public final class DataSet
extends java.lang.Object
    The Database of the information system. inclGraph is the inclusion graph proper. getClassNames() returns a sorted list of all class names.
